# Local development environment. Copy to .env (which is gitignored) and fill in.
#
# In debug builds, when ZFIROT_GITHUB_TOKEN is set the app reads the token from
# the environment instead of the OS keychain, so repeated `dx serve` rebuilds do
# not re-trigger the keychain prompt. `make dev` / `make run` load this .env
# automatically. Leave it unset to use the OS secure store (always so in release).
#
# Use a fine-grained PAT (Issues read/write, Pull requests read, Contents read).
ZFIROT_GITHUB_TOKEN=github_pat_...
